From 2ae1970eec37ae8be318c838c58f9dfd4f9b6ccf Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: zsy-jason <186247581+zsy-jason@users.noreply.github.com>
Date: Wed, 15 Apr 2026 16:40:24 +0800
Subject: [PATCH] feat(macos): implement hybrid composition overlay 
 pipeline(Phase 1+2)

Add macOS platform overlay and presenter services that allow Lynx/Skia
UI layers to render on top of native NSViews (Scintilla, etc.) using
CALayer-based overlay composition.
Key changes:
- Add LynxOverlayView (NSView + CAMetalLayer) as overlay surface
- Add PlatformOverlayServiceMac / PresenterServiceMac implementations
- Register overlay services in LynxUIRenderer on the main thread
- Enable SupportHybridComposition() in NativeViewPluginDesktop
- Fix CompositorService::OnInit to not call GetService early (race
  condition: macOS Create() returns non-null, causing FML_DCHECK abort
  when RegisterService is later called); use lazy re-query in SubmitFrame
- Add service_manager_weak_ for lazy service resolution after init
Co-Authored-By: Claude Sonnet 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>
